{"type": "article", "id": 8214, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-04-08T07:57:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4076, "name": "婴儿车"}, {"id": 8644, "name": "自助理发镜"}, {"id": 8645, "name": "浴室用品"}, {"id": 8646, "name": "甲壳虫概念车"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 7363, "name": "大众"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604224313PntKNbligG0MZCpu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tTrio Love by Stefano Giovannoni\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t意大利儿童品牌 Chicco 邀请著名产品设计师 Stefano Giovannoni 为其设计了一款新型婴儿车。这款名为 “Trio Love”（三口之爱）的婴儿车旨在既给宝宝提供舒适和安全的环境，又满足父母们在实用功能上的需求，追求轻便、稳定性和方便性。设计师从运动学的角度入手，调整了手推车的重量和体积，车身采用铝制材料，精致而又牢固，配备有汽车标准的安全保险杠以保证安全性。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224259sq8b6UJW5NQxYR3i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224259wezvEsQyxtB8gc5G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87652812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224300OoJUDSi2XRj0sCcd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.07090465\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<em style=\"white-space:normal;\">可以折叠的婴儿车 Passeggino Chicco Love</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224300acJi2vUDox5GslN1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5620915\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224301MopAqj2dYPkZNgC3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.54054054\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><em>Navicella Chicco Love 提篮</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042243017BlkvxuQYWFIoT3p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54054054\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224302iaT8rwtFnW3O01le.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5620915\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<em>Seggiolino Oasys 0+ 适合新生儿的小型提篮，可以稳固在汽车座位上。</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tSpecial Edition Concepts by Volkswagen Beetle\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t在 2015 年纽约车展中，大众发布了 4 款甲壳虫概念车，分别为涂有 Stonewashed Blue金属车漆的 Convertible Denim，拉风的敞篷车Convertible Wave，主打运动风格，涂有 Oryx White珍珠漆的 R-line 和粉色的 Pink Color Edition。其中 Convertible Denim 采用软顶敞篷，而 Pink Color Edition，这款直接以颜色命名的概念车，主要是用来满足北美以及中国市场对于粉色甲壳虫的需求。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042243022FI1KlA7pvOEkVgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56266667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224303ZOokaUR4gG3l6xbp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56266667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224304pegDksu5NbZEvWQU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56266667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224304SKjMd5Ogz4G7aWhc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56266667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224305XkefGPgIKL5lHszm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56266667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tEconomical Chair by Seungji Mun \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t韩国设计师 Seungji Mun 继推出呼吁“零浪费”的<a href=\"http://www.munseungji.com/#!four-brothers/c1s6c\" target=\"_blank\">“四兄弟”系列椅子</a>之后，又推出了“经济型椅子”，意在最大限度减少工业浪费。这一款椅子采用单片胶合板，只需要胶合板弯曲就可以形成椅子的形状，在大规模生产中几乎不造成浪费，同时降低了成本。椅子有三色可选，且方便堆叠。这是<a href=\"http://www.munseungji.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，可以看到他更多的作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224305e1hMy3DfZWax7nQP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224306gb8R3HNJdDEI9UeM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224306tLYfVkExTK06ihsr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224307nIBNQsAtycFiXl2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224307YMnVc1ZOlzukNoXr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224307FvYgGdrwCbK2V6e3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tSelf－Barber Mirror by GolfJC \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t泰国设计师 GolfJC 设计的这一款自助理发镜子专门解决那些试图自己剪发者的苦恼，这款镜子有两个可以折叠的面，镜面可以呈任何角度旋转，可以允许你看见不同角度的自己。而在镜子后面，还有一个隐藏的隔层用来存放剪刀，梳子等理发工具，使用起来非常方便。这个泰国设计师的设计风格以简约明快为基调，这是<a href=\"http://www.golfjc.com/GOLFJC/WORK.html\" target=\"_blank\">她的个人主页。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042243083IGxPEdMyKDAp0N7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32151589\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224308pX03xwfmeR4ntiZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14914425\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042243097L6ASldg30Zjn9ay.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31173594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224309yImJfc5hXzdGbDeP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224310hWrQUPCSsYVd8EJk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.52567237\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tCollection of Bathroom by Norm Architects \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t丹麦设计工作室 Norm Architects 最近推出了一个浴室用品系列，包括一个浴缸，一个洗脸盆，一个储物架和一组吊灯。该设计遵循极简主义原则，浴缸和洗脸盆采用同样的形状。整套产品采用一种叫做 “Living Tec”的轻质新型材料，底部则由十字交叉形的黑色支架支撑，简单明快又不失优雅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224310xb3ygMKX6I1vTnOH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224311ZcJUsEPNg1Op3WbG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224311Z6uLFeH8kaBxOUCc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224311Msb91yJ6cUIPHGCA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042243129sfDbRmueyaqAnFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33480176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224312WNUD65LpB7SJHkVs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98913043\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}